Device::CableModem::Motorola::SB4200
====================================

Interface to Motorola SurfBoard 4200 Cable Modem.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

Alternatively, you can use the Build.PL

   perl Build.PL
   perl Build
   perl Build test
   perl Build install

DEPENDENCIES

   LWP::UserAgent
   HTML::TableParser
   HTML::Form
   Exception::Class

BUILD DEPENDENCIES

   Test::More

